data.description:
Immaculate and well maintained single-story in the heart of desirable and famous Green Valley Ranch. This a great  home for early retirement and active living. Front room was converted to a home office with sitting area. The largest room was converted to a home gym with full length mirrors and a wall mounted TV. The kitchen has been completely remodeled with granite counter tops, solid maple cabinetry and travertine floors. Large sliding glass doors, from the adjacent dinning area, lead you to the private backyard with mountain views. Easy care desert landscape in back and lush green lawn in front.  Walk to Discovery Park, The District upscale shopping, and multi-generational facility.  Just, 2 miles, to 215 & 95 freeway access. Extremely quiet location adjacent to age restricted golf course community.

Neighborhood Description

Green Valley Ranch is a 1,310 acre master-planned community located in Henderson, Nevada.  It was created by the American Nevada Corporation.  Construction began in 1995.  The community features a carefully planned mix of land with 775 acres of residential neighborhoods and 310 acres of retail, office, medical facilities, and a resort hotel & spa.  More than 200 acres are parks, schools, recreational centers, open space areas, pedestrian and bike paths, and houses of worship.
data.whatILove: Perfect location within famous Green Valley Ranch in Henderson, NV.  Low master plan fees, and great local events.
